  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Seafood Gumbo</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Seafood Gumbo</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> recipe introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC. It requires more than 2.0 units of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fish</a>.\n</p><p>Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a> will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ceviche\" title=\"Ceviche\">Ceviche</a> instead, unless a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wobster\" title=\"Wobster\">Wobster</a> is also added, which will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lobster_Bisque\" title=\"Lobster Bisque\">Lobster Bisque</a>. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> value 2.5 or higher will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Surf_%27n%27_Turf\" title=\"Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf\">Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf</a> instead. Adding a Wobster and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter\" title=\"Butter\">Butter</a> will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lobster_Dinner\" title=\"Lobster Dinner\">Lobster Dinner</a> instead. Adding exactly 2 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\">Seaweed</a> will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/California_Roll\" title=\"California Roll\">California Roll</a> instead. Adding a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shark_Fin\" title=\"Shark Fin\">Shark Fin</a> will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shark_Fin_Soup\" title=\"Shark Fin Soup\">Shark Fin Soup</a> instead. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Barnacles\" title=\"Barnacles\">Barnacles</a> will yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Stuffed_Fish_Heads\" title=\"Stuffed Fish Heads\">Stuffed Fish Heads</a> instead. Adding Meats value 1.5 or higher and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tallbird_Egg\" title=\"Tallbird Egg\">Tallbird Egg</a> or Fried Tallbird Egg may yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bacon_and_Eggs\" title=\"Bacon and Eggs\">Bacon and Eggs</a> instead. Adding more than one <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Food\" title=\"Monster Food\">Monster Foods</a>, such as <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Jellyfish\" title=\"Jellyfish\">Jellyfish</a>, may yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Lasagna\" title=\"Monster Lasagna\">Monster Lasagna</a> instead. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corn\" title=\"Corn\">Corn</a>, single <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twig\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Twig\">Twig</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\">Mandrake</a> may respectively yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos\" title=\"Fish Tacos\">Fish Tacos</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a> instead.\n</p><p>In DST, using at least 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eel\" title=\"Eel\">Eel</a> is mandatory, otherwise the resulting meal will be Surf &#x27;n&#x27; Turf which requires 2.5 Meat value. Currently, Eel is the only Fish with a Meat value inferior to its Fish value.\n</p><p>It restores 40 Health, 37.5 Hunger and 20 Sanity. The Health and Hunger restoration is comparable to <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a>, though the Sanity restoration is much higher. Seafood Gumbo can be given to the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Yaarctopus\" title=\"Yaarctopus\">Yaarctopus</a> in exchange for a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sail#Cloth_Sail\" title=\"Sail\">Cloth Sail</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires:<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes_Crock_Pot.png?7aa195\" width=\"525\" height=\"110\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"_Recipes\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cookbook.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipes</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>&gt;<b>2.0</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo\" title=\"Seafood Gumbo\"><img alt=\"Seafood Gumbo.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seafood_Gumbo.png?23fc0d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Raw_Fish\" title=\"Raw Fish\"><img alt=\"Raw Fish.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Raw_Fish.png?c251a7\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limpets\" title=\"Limpets\"><img alt=\"Limpets.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limpets.png?c18778\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berries\" title=\"Berries\"><img alt=\"Berries.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berries.png?629a2e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo\" title=\"Seafood Gumbo\"><img alt=\"Seafood Gumbo.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seafood_Gumbo.png?23fc0d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tropical_Fish\" title=\"Tropical Fish\"><img alt=\"Tropica