<td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limpets\" title=\"Limpets\"><img alt=\"Limpets.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limpets.png?c18778\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo\" title=\"Seafood Gumbo\"><img alt=\"Seafood Gumbo.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seafood_Gumbo.png?23fc0d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>50% chance to yield <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roe.png?f773e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Limpets\" title=\"Limpets\"><img alt=\"Limpets.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Limpets.png?c18778\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo\" title=\"Seafood Gumbo\"><img alt=\"Seafood Gumbo.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seafood_Gumbo.png?23fc0d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Exchange\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dubloons\" title=\"Dubloons\"><img alt=\"Dubloons.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dubloons.png/32px-Dubloons.png?5bbf28\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Exchange</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo\" title=\"Seafood Gumbo\"><img alt=\"Seafood Gumbo.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seafood_Gumbo.png?23fc0d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Yaarctopus_Icon\" title=\"Yaarctopus Icon\"><img alt=\"Yaarctopus Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Yaarctopus_Icon.png/42px-Yaarctopus_Icon.png?9466be\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cloth_Sail\" title=\"Cloth Sail\"><img alt=\"Cloth Sail.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cloth_Sail.png?543872\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Seafood Gumbo was introduced to <i>Don&#x27;t Starve Together</i> in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Return_of_Them#Version_History\" title=\"Return of Them\">Hook, Line, and Inker</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seafood_Gumbo#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
