  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Gumbo Hải Sản là một công thức Nồi Hầm được giới thiệu trong DLC ​​Shipwrecked. Nó đòi hỏi hơn 2,0 đơn vị Cá.</p>",
  "title": "Seafood Gumbo",
  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Exclusivity|Shipwrecked|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Seafood Gumbo.png\n|image = Seafood Gumbo Dropped.png\n|hpRestored     = 40\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 20\n|cooktime       = 20 sec\n|priority       = 10\n|spoil          = 10 Days\n|stack          = 40\n|spawnCode      = \"seafoodgumbo\"\n|canBeBurned=1\n|foodType = [[Food Type#Meat|Meat]] {{Pic|32px|Meats|Food Type#Meat}}\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Fishes}}>2 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2-1\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = It's a jumbo seafood gumbo.\n|willow = Ew, what IS this?\n|wolfgang = This will make very strong Wolfgang!\n|wendy = A sea once teeming with life. No more.\n|wx78 = READY FOR INGESTION\n|wickerbottom = I can feel the heartburn already!\n|woodie = We don't have this back home.\n|maxwell = It looks passable.\n|wagstaff = Still contains the skeletal remains of a fish.\n|wigfrid = A meal fit för a queen.\n|webber = We could eat it forever!\n|walani = My favorite!\n|warly = Incredible! Just like Nana used to make!\n|woodlegs = Down th'hatch!\n|wilba = 'TIS EATS O' THE SEA\n|wormwood = Mmm...\n|wheeler = Swell. Fish bones soup.\n|winona = Sticks to yer ribs!\n|wortox = Gleefully gilly gumbo!\n|wurt = Fish looks so sad in there...\n|walter = Packed full of flavour!\n|wanda = Again... is leaving the bones in really necessary?\n|choose = webber\n}}\n'''Seafood Gumbo''' is a [[Crock Pot]] recipe introduced in the ''[[Don't Starve: Shipwrecked|Shipwrecked]]'' DLC. It requires more than 2.0 units of [[Fishes|Fish]].\n\nAdding [[Ice]] will yield [[Ceviche]] instead, unless a [[Wobster]] is also added, which will yield [[Lobster Bisque]]. Adding [[Meats]] value 2.5 or higher will yield [[Surf 'n' Turf]] instead. Adding a Wobster and [[Butter]] will yield [[Lobster Dinner]] instead. Adding exactly 2 [[Seaweed]] will yield [[California Roll]] instead. Adding a [[Shark Fin]] will yield [[Shark Fin Soup]] instead. Adding [[Barnacles]] will yield [[Stuffed Fish Heads]] instead. Adding Meats value 1.5 or higher and [[Tallbird Egg]] or Fried Tallbird Egg may yield [[Bacon and Eggs]] instead. Adding more than one [[Monster Food]]s, such as [[Jellyfish]], may yield [[Monster Lasagna]] instead. Adding [[Corn]], single [[Twig]] or [[Mandrake]] may respectively yield [[Fish Tacos]], [[Fishsticks]] or [[Mandrake Soup]] instead.\n\nIn DST, using at least 1 [[Eel]] is mandatory, otherwise the resulting meal will be Surf 'n' Turf which requires 2.5 Meat value. Currently, Eel is the only Fish with a Meat value inferior to its Fish value.\n\nIt restores 40 Health, 37.5 Hunger and 20 Sanity. The Health and Hunger restoration is comparable to [[Fishsticks]], though the Sanity restoration is much higher. Seafood Gumbo can be given to the [[Yaarctopus]] in exchange for a [[Sail#Cloth Sail|Cloth Sail]].\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n* Requires:[[File:Fishes Crock Pot.png|link=Fishes]]\n\n== [[File:Cookbook.png|32px]] Recipes ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|count1 = 2.0\n|comparator1 = >\n|item2 = Filler\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo\n}}\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|item2 = Raw Fish\n|item3 = Limpets\n|item4 = Berries\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Tropical Fish\n|item2 = Dead Jellyfishes\n|item3 = Mussels\n|item4 = Seaweed\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Wobster\n|item2 = Limpets\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Dead Jellyfishes\n|item2 = Mussels\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Jellyfish\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Limpets\n|item3 = Twigs\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo\n|note=50% chance to yield [[Fishsticks]].\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Roe\n|item2 = Limpets\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Seafood Gumbo}}\n== {{Pic32|Dubloons}} Exchange ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Seafood Gumbo\n|tool = Yaarctopus Icon\n|result = Cloth Sail\n}}\n\n== {{pic32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Seafood Gumbo was introduced to ''Don't Starve Together'' in the ''[[Return of Them#Version History|Hook, Line, and Inker]]'' update.\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[fr:Gumbo de la mer]]\n[[vi:Súp Mướp Tây Hải Sản]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Food]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]"
}
